is capable of supporting strong collaboration. However, since a single
group did not display high scores in all five metrics, we cannot say that
AEN does support strong collaboration.  There could be some odd interaction
between the five major features of AEN that does not allow a group to score
high in all five metrics.  Chapter \ref{sec:analysis} explores the results
of the case study in detail.
